      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p><persName ref="#wazirKhan">Wazir Khan</persName> orders that since <persName ref="#hariram">Hariram</persName>, landlord (chaudhri) of district <placeName ref="#amjhera">Amjhera</placeName>, failed to turn up
               to pay the spring season's taxes, his possessions now belong to his guarantors <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>, <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>, and others. The guarantors are obliged to make the revenue payments for the district.
            </p>
